# Placeholder so the build context always contains this directory.
#
# The deploy workflow (.github/workflows/pulumi-infra.yml) builds the private
# `heliosos` enterprise plugin wheel from makingscience-awake/heliosos-enterprise
# (using the HELIOSOS_ENTERPRISE_TOKEN Actions secret) and drops it here before
# submitting the Cloud Build. The Dockerfile builder installs any wheel found in
# this dir. When no token/wheel is present the image builds in open-source mode
# (the enterprise package is simply absent → bootstrap/urls fall back via their
# existing `except ImportError`). Actual *.whl files are gitignored.
